      "value": "Erase your Brainwave Clock and deal damage."
    },
    "description": "<blockquote><p>Requirements: you must have mastered the <strong>Esper</strong> Class.</p></blockquote><p>While your <strong>Brainwave Clock</strong> is <strong>full</strong>, you may use an action to erase all of its sections. If you do, you may choose one option: you deal @DMG[20 physical] damage to every enemy that is present on the scene; <strong>or</strong> you deal @DMG[30 physical] damage to a single enemy you can see. This amount increases by 10 if you are <strong>level 20 or higher</strong>, or by 20 if you are <strong>level 40 or higher.</strong></p><hr /><ul><li><p><strong>Reset:</strong> @CLOCK[brainwave-clock reset]{Reset Brainwave Clock}</p></li><li><p><strong>Target Loses:</strong> @DMG[&amp;step(20,30,40) physical]{20|30|40 physical (single)}, or @DMG[&amp;step(30,40,50) physical]{30|40|50 physical (multi)}</p><p></p></li></ul>",
